summary: This is a little Collection of performance Boosting Files that will make you skyrim run smoother.
descriptionHtml:
==========Installation=======
Easily put everything inside this Folder in the Skyrim folder were the TESV.exe is located.
Put the d3d9.dll and the enbhost.exe from the enbbinarys wrapper version in the Skyrim folder to.
[url]http://www.enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0254.html[url] here you will get them :)
If a text with enbseries appears in the left upper corner evrything worked
Have fun and enjoy a smoother skyrim and feel free to write me a message if you have problems with this mod :)
